genresAdvancedInfo.name: vispop
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Vispop is a popular music genre in the Philippines that features upbeat and catchy tunes. The songs are usually about love, relationships, and everyday life. The music videos often showcase beautiful locations and vibrant colors, making them visually appealing. Vispop has become a cultural phenomenon in the Philippines and has gained a massive following among the younger generation.
